# --- DVLA Vehicle Enquiry API (registration lookup on Sell / Part exchange) ---
# Portal (all APIs): https://developer-portal.driver-vehicle-licensing.api.gov.uk/availableapis.html
# Vehicle Enquiry spec: https://developer-portal.driver-vehicle-licensing.api.gov.uk/apis/vehicle-enquiry-service/vehicle-enquiry-service-description.html
# Project notes: docs/DVLA-API.md
#
# Copy this file to `.env` (gitignored). Never commit real keys.
# Prefer setting dvlaApiKey next to web3formsAccessKey in src/environments/environment.ts;
# use DVLA_API_KEY here if you want the key only on the server / proxy (not in the browser bundle).
#   ng serve:  proxy.conf.cjs loads this `.env` automatically; DVLA returns 403 if no key is sent.
#   Proxy uses x-api-key from the app first, else DVLA_API_KEY from here / the shell.
#   SSR:       server.ts loads `.env` from the project root when you run `npm run serve:ssr:driveline`.
# GitHub Pages: set repo secret DVLA_LOOKUP_URL (Cloudflare Worker URL) — not this file. See workers/dvla-ves-proxy/README.md
DVLA_API_KEY=

# Enquiry forms use Web3Forms (browser). Set the access key in src/environments/environment.ts
# as web3formsAccessKey (local) or GitHub secret WEB3FORMS_ACCESS_KEY for CI — not in .env unless you wire it yourself.
